&lt;/figure>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.jverkamp.com/embeds/books/attachments/hellboy-vol-2-wake-the-devil-x-1.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>It&amp;rsquo;s &lt;a data-goodreads-type="book" data-goodreads-id="102459" href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/102459.hellboy-vol-2-wake-the-devil">Hellboy, Vol. 2: Wake the Devil&lt;/a> and it&amp;rsquo;s EVEN BETTER and EVEN MORE RIDICULOUS!&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Hellboy, Vol. 1: Seed of Destruction</title><link>https://blog.jverkamp.com/2020/04/07/hellboy-vol.-1-seed-of-destruction/</link><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.jverkamp.com/2020/04/07/hellboy-vol.-1-seed-of-destruction/</guid><description>&lt;figure class="cover-image">
