&lt;/figure>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>If I have a real name, I&amp;rsquo;ve never known it. I&amp;rsquo;m called Hellboy.&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>I recently discovered &lt;a href="https://www.comixology.com/">comiXology&lt;/a> (mostly for reading &lt;a data-goodreads-type="book" data-goodreads-id="870" href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/870.fullmetal-alchemist-vol-1">Fullmetal Alchemist, Vol. 1&lt;/a>). Hellboy was one of the comiXology Unlimited suggested reads. Free trial? Let&amp;rsquo;s do it.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>